Jeremy Sarmiento scored in the 40th minute for Ecuador.
Jhonder Cádiz scored in the 64th minute for Venezuela.
Eduard Bello scored in the 74th minute for Venezuela.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Levi's Stadium in Santa Clara, California, USA.

Ecuador had 4 shots on goal while Venezuela had 5 shots on goal.
